text: Miss Universe Australia 2019, the 15th edition of the Miss Universe Australia pageant, was held on June 27, 2019 at Sofitel Melbourne on Collins, Melbourne, Victoria. Francesca Hung of New South Wales crowned Priya Serrao at the end of the event. Serrao will represent Australia at Miss Universe 2019. ==Final results== {| class="wikitable sortable" style="font-size: 95%;" |- ! Final results !
